{
  "stem": "13258.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For more when three people got together on a street corner, they were chased apart by the police.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember that day very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, I have to explain why we lived on Main Street in a big house, which was owned by my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the back of that house were-- was a printing plant from a local newspaper.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in the entrance to the house, which was like a covered driveway, there were glass vitrines, where the paper always was hang out, the newspaper.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So people were standing there all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had, at that time, art classes, private art classes with a teacher, who would take a couple kids and do something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My mother always wanted us kids to do something, be involved in something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I had art classes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was an art class where my mother suddenly came and said, let's go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Go home.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we did not go the usual way, but she took me into a house on a street, which runs parallel to the street on which we were living.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we went through the house, into the backyard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was a door in a fence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She went to the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And suddenly, we were in the backyard of my grandmother's house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now, that was a big house, my grandmother had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it had two yards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was one front yard, surrounded by buildings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then there was an other backyard, where on the one side, my grandparents had a little piece of garden.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And on the other side, there was a-- some little factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I never knew that there existed a gate there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That-- my mother knew that because she had lived, grown up in that house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So they wouldn't let-- take me to the house from the front.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
